    {
      "id": "36",
      "name": "更多訊息",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "日常對話",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "「就像獵人追蹤獵物...」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "伽祿：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "哼，我一定會像追擊獵物那樣，逐漸擊敗所有的敵人，成為最強的「七聖召喚」牌手...怎麽了，有什麽事嗎？",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話1：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "那就來開始「七聖召喚」吧！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "伽祿（玩家勝利）：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "居然被妳/你逃脫了！沒有關係，妳/你不可能一直都那麽幸運的...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "伽祿（玩家失敗）：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "哼哼，這下，妳/你也成為我捕獲的「獵物」了。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話2：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "不，沒什麽事...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "伽祿：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "哼，等妳/你想要找人一起「七聖召喚」的時候，就來找我吧。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "七聖召喚",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "決鬥對局",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "關卡介紹",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "思考相當敏捷的「七聖召喚」牌手，會如同追捕獵物一樣猛烈地進攻。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "【提示】這是一位強大的牌手，建議牌手等級高一些再來挑戰。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "對手陣容",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3199,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/169177528/920c7d546361d0b52dd95613517319f9_6116404733914419935.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "翠翎恐蕈",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
